 \lim_{x \to -1} \frac{x^2 +3x +2}{x^2 -1} = \lim_{x \to -1} \frac{\frac{x^2}{x^2} + \frac{3x}{x^2} + \frac{2}{x^2}}{\frac{x^2}{x^2} - \frac{1}{x^2}} = \lim_{x \to -1} \frac{\frac{1}{1} + 0 + 0}{\frac{1}{1} - 0} = \lim_{x \to -1} \frac{1}{1} = 1 
